{"word":"περίεργος","slug":"περίεργος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περίεργος</b></el> <el>(περί-εργος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>*<a href='S:ἔργω'><el>ἔργω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>careful overmuch</i>, <b><a href='S:Lysias'>Lys.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>busy about other folk's affairs, meddling, a busybody</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>done with especial care, elaborate</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>superfluous</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>curious, superstitious</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}